      "methodTier": "tier 1",
      "methodModelDescription": "A semi variable approach was taken for the calculation of enteric CH4 emission estimates. Fixed emission factors were used when pasture was the main dietary component for suckler beef cows and other animal classes (IPCC, 2006) (Emission factor (EF) 1). When grass silage comprised the forage component of the diet, the equation of Yan et al. (2000) denoted as EF 2, was used for suckler beef cows, whilst for other animal categories EF 1 was used.",
